'''凱文·皮特森'''（{{lang-en|Kevin Pietersen}}；{{bd|1980年|6月27日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]板球運動員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/cricket/article5683117.ece|title=Kevin Pietersen: Dumbslog millionaire|date=8 February 2009|work=The Sunday Times|accessdate=28 February 2009 | location=London | first=Simon | last=Wilde}}</ref>。他是一位右手球員，出生在南非。凱文曾代表[[英格蘭板球代表隊|英格蘭板球代表隊]]參賽。在2018年末退役。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/cricket/kevin-pietersen-to-retire-from-cricket-20180106-h0ei37.html|title=Kevin Pietersen to retire from all forms of cricket|last=Cherny|first=Daniel|date=2018-01-07|newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2018-01-06|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107105751/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/cricket/kevin-pietersen-to-retire-from-cricket-20180106-h0ei37.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
